body:
### Is your feature request related to a problem?

I need to calculate bounds of a picture as follows:

```cs
static SkRect CalculateApproximateLocalBounds(const SkPicture& picture) {
	SkRTreeFactory factory;
	SkPictureRecorder recorder;
	SkCanvas* pictureCanvas = recorder.beginRecording(SkIntToScalar(1000000), SkIntToScalar(1000000), &factory);
	picture.playback(pictureCanvas);
	return recorder.finishRecordingAsPicture()->cullRect();
}
```
With SkiaSharp i am missing SkPicture::playback() API. I hope this one gets exposed before the release of SkiaSharp 3.0.

### Describe the solution you would like
```cs
public static class SKPictureExtensions
{
  public static void Playback(this SKPicture skPicture, SKCanvas skCanvas);
}
```

### Describe alternatives you have considered

N/A

